From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: EBAZ4205 BSP <ebaz4205@example.invalid>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] arm: dts: build zynq-ebaz4205 DTB

The board DTS is supplied by the EBAZ4205 Yocto layer. Add its output to
the Zynq DTB list so U-Boot's arch-dtbs target actually builds it before
dts/Makefile checks for the selected DEVICE_TREE.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [board-specific]

Signed-off-by: EBAZ4205 BSP <ebaz4205@example.invalid>
---
 arch/arm/dts/Makefile | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
index 6bb96f1e42a..bf099c47f91 100644
--- a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
@@ -223,6 +223,7 @@ dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_UNIPHIER_SLD8) += \
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_ZYNQ) += \
 	bitmain-antminer-s9.dtb \
 	zynq-cc108.dtb \
+	zynq-ebaz4205.dtb \
 	zynq-cse-nand.dtb \
 	zynq-cse-nor.dtb \
 	zynq-cse-qspi-single.dtb \
-- 
2.43.0

